About this item

  • 【Notice】Buyers should thoroughly examine the installation and wiring instructions depicted in the images before buying. It is recommended to exercise caution if you lack experience in installation to avoid potential problems like product malfunction or incompatibility due to incorrect purchases. Note that the base can only be attached with a maximum of 2 to 5 wires, and connections with 6 to 8 wires are not suitable.
  • 【Compatible Systems】Single-Stage Gas/Oil/Electric Furnace (Heat only) , Boiler Radiant (Heat only), Furnace Forced-Air (Heat Only), Gas Fireplace (24 Volts) and Cooling Only
  • 【Incompatible Systems】Does Not Work: Multistage Heat & Cool; 3-wire Hydronic (Hot Water); HVAC Central Air Conditioner Heat Pump System (with Auxiliary Heating or w/o Auxiliary Heating); Dual Fuel/Hybrid Multistage Heating; Mini Split Systems; RV Thermostat; Convectors, Radiant Ceiling Heat and Electric Baseboard Heat ( 120-240 Volts).
  • Heagstat H701 Non-programmable thermostat for house conventional single-stage systems up to 1 heat/1 cool, to control the temperature in a room.
  • Accurate temperature control of +/-1-Degree F for consistent comfort, Room temperature display range: 41°F to 95°F, Temperature control range: 44°F to 90°F.
  • Separate Heating and Cooling Swing (Cycle Rate). Which will Either Prolong or Shorten the Temperature Open Time. Make Comfortable Temperatures to Teduce Energy Usage, Savings on Annual Heating and Cooling Costs.
  • Support room temperature error display calibration adjustment and 5 minute compressor delay protection (Selectable on or off), with low battery indicator available change reminder (Tip: Please replace the accessories in advance).
  • Support Dual Powered 24VAC Power or 2 AAA Batteries. No Common Wire (c-wire) Rrequired on Most Single-Stage Systems.
  • Display with White Backlight, Easy-to See and Read. Large, Clear Backlit Digital Display, Very Suitable for Middle-Aged and Elderly People.
  • After-sales Service: If you have any problem, please feel free to contact us, we will repley you in 24 hours. the products come with 30 days free return, 2-year Worry-Free Warranty.

    Product Description

    Precautions for products

    1. Confirm whether the product is compatible with your system,

    2. Confirm the size of the product to see if it can cover the traces left on the wall of the old thermostat.

    3. If you encounter installation and troubleshooting problems, please feel free to contact, we will repley you in 24 hours.

    This is a 24VAC conventional single-stage system non-programmable thermostat for home

    Heagstat specializes in the design and manufacturing of professional grade products that improve the comfort of a home and simplify the installation. This H701 non-programmable digital thermostat has many convenient features. Some of its features include: backlit display easy to read, simple operation with slide switches selecting heat or cool mode operating the fan. This thermostat is compatible with single-stage heating/cooling systems, heating, cooling.

    Specifications:

    • Single Stage
    • 1 Heat, 1 Cool
    • Non-programmable
    • large LCD display with white backlight
    • Fan switch with ON and AUTO functions
    • Low battery indicator
    • Electric or Gas configurable
    • Separate B & O terminals
    • Separate heating and cooling swing (cycle rate) adjustments

    • Room temperature calibration adjustment
    • 5 minute compressor delay protection (selectable on or off)
    • Display options: Fahrenheit or Celsius temperature display
    • Product Dimensions: 0.98"D x 4.72"W x 3.86"H

    Easy to see and read

    • 3 Inches large LCD display
    • One-button wake-up white backlight lights
    • Suitable for Middle-Aged and Elderly People.

    Easy to use and install

    • Easy wire coded terminal blocks
    • Terminal Designations RH, RC, G, Y, C, O, B, W
    • Universal sub-base, mounts on wall or junction box
    • Easy access battery compartment
    • Dual-powered (AAA battery and/or hardwire 24VAC power)

    Notice：Should thoroughly examine the installation and wiring instructions depicted in the images before. ( Note that the base can only be attached with a maximum of 2 to 5 wires, and connections with 6 to 8 wires are not suitable.)

    What's in the box?

    • Heagstat H701 thermostat and base (Jumper wire connected)
    • Two screws and anchors
    • Installation manual
    • Cable label

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Amazon Customer
    5 out of 5 stars
    Works Perfectly
    I was looking for a simple non-programmable thermostat to replace the programmable one we had that was malfunctioning. I first purchased a Honeywell brand non programmable one that looked a little sleeker than this one. However, it only had what seemed like a half degree differential and it was causing my furnace to short cycle (6-8 minutes). I ordered this thermostat in hopes that it would work as intended. It works exactly how it should and no more short cycling! This thermostat was easy to install by reading the manual. It looks great and the large display with green backlight is easy to read. I compared the temperature to an indoor thermometer and it was spot on. I appreciate the simplicity of the thermostat and I’m glad that I don’t have to fight with complicated programming. The wiring to my furnace only contains 3 wires and is unable to support modern smart thermostats. So if you need a simple thermostat or are replacing an older thermostat, this is an excellent option. My only complaint would be that it doesn’t come with a wall/back plate. But they do have one available to purchase separately and I will be ordering that next.
